1
00:00:00,468 --> 00:00:04,992
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:04,992 --> 00:00:10,496
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,496 --> 00:00:16,924
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,924 --> 00:00:21,404
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,404 --> 00:00:25,852
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,852 --> 00:00:30,763
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,763 --> 00:00:34,812
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,812 --> 00:00:39,347
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,347 --> 00:00:43,644
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,644 --> 00:00:48,409
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,409 --> 00:00:51,900
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,900 --> 00:00:55,580
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,226 --> 00:01:00,604
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,604 --> 00:01:03,136
=Episode 16=

15
00:01:03,300 --> 00:01:08,633
(He's run the company with threats
and tyranny since becoming the CEO.)

16
00:01:28,433 --> 00:01:32,200
There's more.

17
00:01:32,864 --> 00:01:34,080
Doesn't it end?

18
00:01:36,133 --> 00:01:37,056
Surveillance.

19
00:01:40,833 --> 00:01:43,872
Here we go. Look here.
Lower your head a bit.

20
00:01:44,448 --> 00:01:46,166
Alright, go.

21
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:48,233
What should I do?

22
00:01:48,233 --> 00:01:50,166
Just read the script.

23
00:01:51,866 --> 00:01:52,899
Cut.

24
00:01:53,966 --> 00:01:55,040
Let's start it.

25
00:01:56,766 --> 00:01:59,899
I-I-I am Lan Chen.

26
00:01:59,899 --> 00:02:00,800
Wait.

27
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:02,633
Didn't you say you were going
to clap the board first?

28
00:02:02,633 --> 00:02:04,033
I forgot.

29
00:02:04,033 --> 00:02:04,832
Hurry up.

30
00:02:04,832 --> 00:02:05,833
Come on.

31
00:02:05,900 --> 00:02:06,733
Okay, go.

32
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:10,633
Yes, I'm Lan Chen.

33
00:02:10,733 --> 00:02:11,733
Lan of Lan Chen.

34
00:02:12,736 --> 00:02:14,566
You're not showing
the right emotion. Again.

35
00:02:16,512 --> 00:02:17,233
Go.

36
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,400
Roll it.

37
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:20,900
Yes, it's Lan Chen.

38
00:02:20,900 --> 00:02:23,900
His surname is Lan,
and the first name is Chen.

39
00:02:23,900 --> 00:02:26,000
Just read the script.

40
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:28,366
Just read it as it is.
You don't need to improvise.

41
00:02:28,700 --> 00:02:29,533
Okay, go.

42
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:31,400
Start.

43
00:02:31,566 --> 00:02:32,799
Yes, it's Lv Chen.

44
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,766
His surname is Lan,
and the first name is Chen.

45
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:36,400
What are you doing?

46
00:02:36,433 --> 00:02:37,533
Isn't the emotion right?

47
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:39,700
What? Just read the script.

48
00:02:39,733 --> 00:02:41,333
Just read it.

49
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,100
Just it?

50
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:42,933
Just read it.

51
00:02:43,033 --> 00:02:43,968
Okay.

52
00:02:43,968 --> 00:02:45,120
No additions.

53
00:02:46,466 --> 00:02:51,299
Yes, it's Lan Chen. His surname is Lan,
and the first name is Chen.

54
00:02:51,366 --> 00:02:53,633
H-H-He's run

55
00:02:53,966 --> 00:02:57,666
the company

56
00:02:58,336 --> 00:03:00,866
with threats and intimidation.

57
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,000
Cut.

58
00:03:05,166 --> 00:03:06,266
It's finally finished.

59
00:03:06,500 --> 00:03:08,466
Does this count as my debut?

60
00:03:08,466 --> 00:03:10,266
If you can debut,
we'll have to become monks.

61
00:03:10,366 --> 00:03:12,499
Hurry up. Cut a video.

62
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:15,066
The press conference
will be held tomorrow morning.

63
00:03:15,166 --> 00:03:18,000
Mei Xiangfa,
didn't you find a film editor?

64
00:03:18,566 --> 00:03:20,233
Think of something now.

65
00:03:20,566 --> 00:03:23,033
Why is it always me?
What should I think of?

66
00:03:23,033 --> 00:03:24,299
I-I-I have no idea.

67
00:03:25,566 --> 00:03:27,399
I thought we would have it in one take.

68
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,100
But we had so many NGs.

69
00:03:29,500 --> 00:03:30,766
Find an editor.

70
00:03:31,633 --> 00:03:32,433
What?

71
00:03:32,666 --> 00:03:34,233
Why are you all looking at me?

72
00:03:34,233 --> 00:03:36,366
Where can I find an editor
in the middle of the night?

73
00:03:36,633 --> 00:03:38,699
No one will watch it if it's this long.

74
00:03:39,033 --> 00:03:40,133
Actually,

75
00:03:41,866 --> 00:03:44,033
I also do post-production editing.

76
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:46,033
Let me see.

77
00:03:46,033 --> 00:03:46,799
Take a look.

78
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,900
You are talented.

79
00:03:48,666 --> 00:03:50,966
Start work now.
What are you dawdling for?

80
00:03:51,033 --> 00:03:53,566
You shall pay up first,
as it's an urgent order.

81
00:03:54,266 --> 00:03:55,800
Urgent orders shall be paid in full.

82
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:01,766
Buddy.

83
00:04:01,866 --> 00:04:04,448
When have we ever been short of money?
Money is no problem.

84
00:04:05,248 --> 00:04:06,733
B-But it'll take a few days to pay you.

85
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,800
Right.

86
00:04:07,900 --> 00:04:11,233
We'll talk about it later.
Can you cut it first? We're in a hurry.

87
00:04:11,400 --> 00:04:14,433
Then copy it to a flash drive
and deliver it to this place.

88
00:04:16,566 --> 00:04:19,499
This place. You must do it quickly.

89
00:04:19,500 --> 00:04:20,000
OK.

90
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:20,866
Hurry up.

91
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:22,200
Don't dawdle. Do it now.

92
00:04:22,300 --> 00:04:24,700
I will. Bye, take care.

93
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:26,299
Take care. Go.

94
00:04:31,266 --> 00:04:33,366
Thank goodness this surveillance camera
wasn't discovered.

95
00:04:35,966 --> 00:04:38,099
Love you, Miss Jin.

96
00:04:56,500 --> 00:05:00,166
I found it. This can prove
Lan Chen was slandered.

97
00:05:00,166 --> 00:05:02,566
These things can't fully prove
that Lan Chen didn't cook the books.

98
00:05:02,733 --> 00:05:03,648
I'll prove it.

99
00:05:24,266 --> 00:05:25,433
Ladies and gentlemen,

100
00:05:28,266 --> 00:05:31,166
a few days ago, someone stole my phone.

101
00:05:31,433 --> 00:05:33,366
A bill was sent to my phone.

102
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,033
It was a very advanced method.

103
00:05:36,433 --> 00:05:39,699
If it hadn't been for that,
I'd have found out who sent it to me.

104
00:05:41,066 --> 00:05:42,720
We have arranged
for someone to investigate.

105
00:05:43,466 --> 00:05:45,699
Although WE Beauty Group's products

106
00:05:45,900 --> 00:05:47,433
have not been perfect in recent years,

107
00:05:47,766 --> 00:05:50,299
they have always firmly occupied
more than half of the market share.

108
00:05:50,566 --> 00:05:53,466
It's not nearly as bad
as the bill suggested.

109
00:05:54,766 --> 00:05:56,299
So I guess someone did this

110
00:05:56,566 --> 00:05:59,599
just to deter me from investing in them.

111
00:06:03,233 --> 00:06:04,966
Miss Jin gave me a market data report,

112
00:06:05,066 --> 00:06:08,166
which is very detailed
and comprehensive.

113
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:11,133
Xi'en, wake up.

114
00:06:11,166 --> 00:06:13,566
Do a real market data survey right away.

115
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,032
We have conducted
relevant investigations and research,

116
00:06:20,666 --> 00:06:22,366
and our conclusion is still the same.

117
00:06:23,872 --> 00:06:26,499
Although WE Beauty Group
is a family business

118
00:06:27,033 --> 00:06:28,399
with an unscientific corporate system,

119
00:06:28,400 --> 00:06:30,333
and it has been going downhill
for the past three years,

120
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:35,166
its market brand recognition
and market share remain stable.

121
00:06:35,900 --> 00:06:38,166
I take this opportunity to announce

122
00:06:38,912 --> 00:06:43,168
WE Beauty Group has been among
the top three of our evaluation list.

123
00:06:43,866 --> 00:06:47,066
Mr. Lan, I hope
we can cooperate smoothly.

124
00:06:49,700 --> 00:06:50,500
Besides,

125
00:06:52,500 --> 00:06:53,866
if any of you

126
00:06:54,233 --> 00:06:57,533
report false stories
about Miss Jin and her family,

127
00:06:58,400 --> 00:07:01,700
I won't let him go. Thank you.

128
00:07:16,692 --> 00:07:21,214
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

129
00:07:24,244 --> 00:07:29,205
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

130
00:07:32,254 --> 00:07:38,078
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

131
00:07:38,078 --> 00:07:44,576
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

132
00:07:45,184 --> 00:07:49,029
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

133
00:07:49,029 --> 00:07:53,150
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

134
00:07:53,150 --> 00:07:54,846
♪Open my secret♪

135
00:07:54,846 --> 00:08:00,894
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

136
00:08:00,894 --> 00:08:04,766
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

137
00:08:04,766 --> 00:08:09,272
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

138
00:08:11,264 --> 00:08:17,982
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
